overview: Jep and Shuib scolded Mamat for his stubborn attitude who keeps disturbing their neighbor which is also Jep and Shuib's dream girl. As a result of their argument, Mamat disappeared on the first day of Ramadan. Jep and Shuib tried to look for Mamat and in the search, they find a truck coming out on the side road and have loads of contraband firecrackers. They both forget the purpose of finding Mamat and begin to pay attention to the contraband.
title: Sepahtu Mercun Raya
